hildren":"technical automation"}]," you need to deploy in 2026 to ensure you are always the first person to get paid."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-8","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-outfit border-b-4 border-rose-500 pb-2 inline-block","children":"Strategy 1: The Delivery Dopamine Effect"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg","children":["There is a precise biological moment when a client is most willing to pay you: ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"the moment of delivery."}]," When you deliver a completed project, the client feels a rush of relief and excitement. This is what we call the \"Delivery Dopamine.\""]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-gray-900 text-white p-12 rounded-[3.5rem] shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-black mb-6 text-rose-400","children":"The 24-Hour Rule"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xl mb-6 leading-relaxed","children":["Data from ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Visa Global Business"}]," shows that invoices sent within 24 hours of project completion are paid ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"52% faster"}]," than those sent even 3 days later."]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex gap-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 rounded-full border border-white/20 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest","children":"Speed"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 rounded-full border border-white/20 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest","children":"Momentum"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-2xl p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/10","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm italic opacity-80 mb-4","children":"\"If you wait until Friday to bill for a job you finished on Monday, you have allowed the c